Class AuthnRequestImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.sun.identity.saml2.protocol.impl.RequestAbstractImpl
      • com.sun.identity.saml2.protocol.impl.AuthnRequestImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    AuthnRequest, RequestAbstract
    public class AuthnRequestImpl
extends RequestAbstractImpl
implements AuthnRequest
    The AuthnRequestImpl implements the AuthnRequest interface , defines methods for properties required by a saml request.
